SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (South Slave Region) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (South Slave Region) ORDER to withdraw from disposal the surface and subsurface rights to certain lands for a period ending on November 30, 2014 to facilitate the conclusion of Aboriginal land agreements.
